OL,3,CTeenager who played for Blackburn
OL,4,CRovers and who died in WW2 is
OL,5,Cremembered.
OL,7,FLancashire teenager Alan Bell had a
OL,8,Fpromising football career with
OL,9,FBlackburn Rovers.
OL,11,FInstead the 19-year-old from Lancaster
OL,12,Fdied fighting with the Grenadier
OL,13,FGuards liberating a French village
OL,14,Fduring World War Two.
OL,16,FAlan was the only son of John and
OL,17,FAlice Bell. So devastated were they by
OL,18,Ftheir loss, no-one has ever visited
OL,19,Fhis grave at the Commonwealth War
OL,20,FGrave Cemetery in Lille, Northern
OL,21,FFrance.
