OL,3,CTeenager who played for Blackburn
OL,4,CRovers and who died in WW2 is
OL,5,Cremembered.
OL,7,FThat is until Alan's cousin Pauline
OL,8,FBond from Morecambe made a special
OL,9,Ftrip with her husband to visit his
OL,10,Fgrave back in the 1980's.
OL,12,FPauline is worried as she grows older,
OL,13,Fthere will be no-one to remember
OL,14,FAlan's time with Rovers, and serving
OL,15,Fwith the Grenadier Guards.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
