OL,3,CTeenager who played for Blackburn
OL,4,CRovers and who died in WW2 is
OL,5,Cremembered.
OL,7,FPauline said: "I bought this yellow
OL,8,Fchrysanthemum in a pot, there were all
OL,9,Fthese white graves, and this yellow
OL,10,Fchrysanthemum stood out, because it
OL,11,Fwas the only one there, and it was
OL,12,Fjust a focal point with all the white.
OL,13,FI was so glad I took it."
OL,15,FLancashire historian and author Steve
OL,16,FWilliams is working on a project with
OL,17,FBlackburn Rovers to find all the men
OL,18,Fwho played for the team, but also
OL,19,Ffought in conflicts since 1899.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
