OL,3,CTeenager who played for Blackburn
OL,4,CRovers and who died in WW2 is
OL,5,Cremembered.
OL,7,FHe's been helping Pauline find out
OL,8,Fmore information about her cousin.
OL,10,FSteve said: "What I've found is that
OL,11,FRovers saw him as a budding talent,
OL,12,Fand they physically signed him.
OL,14,F"We know that. He was registered with
OL,15,Fthe Football League, as a young player
OL,16,Ffor the future."
OL,18,FGuardsman Alan Bell died on 3
OL,19,FSeptember, 1944, liberating the
OL,20,Fvillage of Pont-a-Marcq near Lille,
OL,21,FFrance.
