OL,5,Cremembered.
OL,7,FHe had landed in Normandy on D-Day
OL,8,Fplus 7 with the Grenadier Guards, and
OL,9,Fwas involved in heavy fighting as the
OL,10,FGuards moved south through towns and
OL,11,Fvillages in Northern France.
